data.description: Great opportunity to own a newly constructed FULLY furnished lake house on Ham Lake with 102 ft of lake shore. This was a full rebuild in 2019, With 4 large Bedrooms(2 non conforming, no  closets) 2 bathrooms, spacious living and dining area, loft, and tons of storage! Enjoy beautiful lake views from each level of the home. The wall- to- wall pine vaulted ceiling's and lake view picture window set up is ideal for individuals who want the most out of their lake home.  This house is turn key ready with everything you would need included! All necessary kitchen items, beds, night stands, tables, rugs TV's,lamps,back up generator,aluminium dock and much more... feel free open the cabinets and drawers it's all included! Large detach garage, maintenance free siding and leaf guard gutters will ensure you waste no time on property upkeep.
